thread.title: Miss Danielle Hacking
thread.title_full: Optimalprint reviewed by Miss Danielle Hacking

author: Miss Danielle Hacking
title: Miss Danielle Hacking
text: Excellent website, so many options to choose from and very easy to use. Pricing is the best around and delivery was so fast! The only fault I could find is that the photos aren't very clear. They were high resolution professional pics so was definately something to do with the printing. If I'd known this I would've paid a higher price to get clearer pictures.
